{"id": "1670515267", "isEnabled": true, "objectTypeId": "0-3", "flowType": "WORKFLOW", "revisionId": "25", "name": "Bot Hook | Construction", "description": "Sends SMS and email updates about the Site Survey phase to customers in Colorado managed by a specific project manager, then triggers a webhook and notifies an internal user.", "uuid": "Bot Hook | Construction-1670515267", "createdAt": "2025-07-10T13:07:32.251Z", "updatedAt": "2026-04-08T19:57:18.137Z", "startActionId": "2", "nextAvailableActionId": "8", "actions": [{"actionId": "1", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-5", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "3"}, "fields": {"property_name": "project_status", "value": {"staticValue": "This is a {{ enrolled_object.project_type }} project worth a contract value of {{ enrolled_object.amount }}. The project stage is {{ enrolled_object.dealstage }}.\n\nThe sales consultant is {{ enrolled_object.hubspot_owner_id }}. \n\nThe project manager is {{ enrolled_object.project_manager }}. \n\nThis project is based out of our {{ enrolled_object.pb_location }} office. \n\nThe address for this job is {{ enrolled_object.address_line_1 }}, {{ enrolled_object.city }}, {{ enrolled_object.state }} {{ enrolled_object.postal_code }}.\n\nThe Authority Having Jurisdiction (AHJ) is {{ fetched_objects.fetched_object_153777980.record_name }}. They take {{ fetched_objects.fetched_object_153777980.permit_turnaround_average }} days to approve permits. \n\nThe utility company for this address is {{ enrolled_object.utility_company }}\n\nThe site survey status is {{ enrolled_object.site_survey_status }}.\n\nThe design approval status is{{ enrolled_object.layout_status }}.\n\nThe design & engineering status is {{ enrolled_object.design_status }}. \n\nThe permit status is {{ enrolled_object.permitting_status }}. The permit submission date is: {{ enrolled_object.permit_submit_date }}. The permit issued date is {{ enrolled_object.permit_completion_date }}. \n\nThe interconnection application status with the utility company is {{ enrolled_object.interconnection_status }}.\n\nThe construction status is {{ enrolled_object.install_status }}. \n\nThe inspection status is {{ enrolled_object.final_inspection_status }}. ", "type": "STATIC_VALUE"}}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}, {"actionId": "2", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-1", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "1"}, "fields": {"delta": "2", "time_unit": "MINUTES"}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}, {"actionId": "3", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-5", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "4"}, "fields": {"property_name": "construction_update___sms", "value": {"staticValue": "Hello, this is Olivia - Virtual Assistant with Photon Brothers. Your permits and utility approvals are in! That means we\u2019re ready to finalize equipment ordering and schedule your installation. Over the next 1-3 weeks, a team member will reach out with preferred dates for our Operations team to install your system. Most installations take 1\u20132 days, depending on system size.\n\nIf your project includes a Tesla Powerwall, please download the Tesla app and have your login email ready\u2014this is important for our team during battery setup.\n\nLet us know if you have any questions. Otherwise, we\u2019ll be in touch soon with scheduling options.\n\nReply END to stop texts.", "type": "STATIC_VALUE"}}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}, {"actionId": "4", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-5", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "6"}, "fields": {"property_name": "construction_update___email", "value": {"staticValue": "Hello, this is Olivia - Virtual Assistant with Photon Brothers.\n\nGreat news: Your permits and utility approvals are in! With all necessary approvals now in place, we are ready to finalize the ordering of your equipment and schedule your installation.\n\nA team member will reach out over the next 1-3 weeks with some preferred dates where our Operations team will come and install your project. Most installations are completed in 1-2 days, depending on the system size.\n\n\nWhat to Expect Next:\n\nWe'll be ordering and receiving your equipment over the next 1\u20132 weeks, which is required before we can begin installation\n\nWe'll contact you to schedule your installation once materials have been secured\n\nOur crew will arrive on the scheduled date to begin the installation\n\nWe\u2019ll handle everything from start to finish to ensure a smooth, efficient process\n\n\nImportant Note:\nIf your system includes a Tesla Powerwall, please download the Tesla app before your installation and have the email address you used to register your account ready when our team arrives. This helps us streamline setup and activation.\n\nWe\u2019re excited to bring your system to life! Please let us know if you have any questions, otherwise, we will be in touch soon with some installation dates.\n\nBest,\nPhoton Brothers", "type": "STATIC_VALUE"}}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}, {"actionId": "5", "method": "POST", "webhookUrl": "https://public.lindy.ai/api/v1/webhooks/lindy/d65c10cb-585b-490e-bac2-75be3b0d875b", "queryParams": [], "authSettings": {"secretName": "lindy_stage_change", "name": "Bearer", "location": "HEADER", "type": "AUTH_KEY"}, "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "7"}, "type": "WEBHOOK"}, {"actionId": "6", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-1", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "5"}, "fields": {"delta": "1", "time_unit": "MINUTES"}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}, {"actionId": "7", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-8", "fields": {"subject": "Bot Construction Webhook Fired - {{ enrolled_object.dealname }}", "body": "<p>Bot Permit Webhook Fired:<br>{{ enrolled_object.dealname }}<br><br><br>{{ fetched_objects.fetched_object_153777981.firstname }} {{ fetched_objects.fetched_object_153777981.lastname }}</p>\n<p>{{ fetched_objects.fetched_obj